{"tid":2342498,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"弟憂鄧棨然重判 委託律師被禁言  家屬促鹽田明直播聆訊","createTime":"2020-12-27T07:38:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T08:25:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"551d4df891c81377079c3a0c13533d10179c1519","tid":2342498,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T07:38:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201227/7NVT3QZKB5FZLL7XWAWS3HZ2SU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201227%2F7NVT3QZKB5FZLL7XWAWS3HZ2SU%2F&d=sZqGLlkYYIxatccyfr7NWBlCv%2FutJLQSKuuf3SGwDjg%3D&h=9effd7bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201227%2F7NVT3QZKB5FZLL7XWAWS3HZ2SU%2F&h=73eb39cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201227/7NVT3QZKB5FZLL7XWAWS3HZ2SU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n弟憂鄧棨然重判 委託律師被禁言 <br />\n家屬促鹽田明直播聆訊<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】涉偷渡台灣但被內地關押的12名港人，經歷四個多月秘密扣押後，其中10人將於明日面對秘密和視像審訊，有家屬要求內地直播審訊，亦有家屬已有心理準備親人或被重判。有家屬受委託的內地律師被通知今次案件敏感，勿隨便發表言論，「以免被別有用心之人士利用藉機炒作」。全國人大常委譚耀宗則大讚內地司法水平有很大改善，相信內地對12港人案會依法做事。<br />\n<br />\n12港人被送中127日，部份家屬前日接獲內地官派律師通知，其中10人將於明日下午2時半，以視像方式於深圳市鹽田區人民法院受審，法院表明審訊將不設旁聽。另外兩名於被捕時未滿18歲的港人，會由檢察院聽證會處理，日期未知。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/xx7HcPJcFBToqbGGylzxe1WCrqE=/1811x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/A3IIQ7CGAJGW5KOJHU325YHMYA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fxx7HcPJcFBToqbGGylzxe1WCrqE%3D%2F1811x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FA3IIQ7CGAJGW5KOJHU325YHMYA.jpg&h=b41096fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■鄧棨然弟弟（右）昨指已有心理準備，哥哥會長時間服刑；圖為鄧弟早前在記者會安慰母親。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n官派律師：刑期一定唔會七年<br />\n<br />\n12港人中，鄧棨然被控組織他人偷越邊境罪，其弟接受本報查詢，指親身聽審是唯一可與獄。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另一被捕人黃偉然的太太稱，前。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n被折騰四個多月，黃太。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n12港人家屬連月來多次請。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n有家屬委託的代表律師指，幾乎所有受12港人家屬委託的律師都被當局約談。有代表律師稱，接獲律師工作委員會的提示，指12港人的案件敏感，所有律師不得隨意評論案件，要保持正確的輿論導向，以免被別有用心的人士藉機炒作。。。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"3193727fd8377febb1e828005ba0729b6896c7e5","tid":2342498,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T07:41:58.000Z","msg":"辛苦家屬了<br />\n<br />\n人生要被國家屈到喊左幾多晚"},{"pid":"d44406f8af653342a8a1951d35d1746175621f16","tid":2342498,"uid":295650,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3193727fd8377febb1e828005ba0729b6896c7e5","tid":2342498,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T07:41:58.000Z","msg":"辛苦家屬了<br />\n<br />\n人生要被國家屈到喊左幾多晚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T07:54:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6478f3a31b1fe05c2d8e5093c2ec4a290cb2020c","tid":2342498,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T08:24:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dfa95214858229dec24b7b9cb3cba41a6f11299","tid":2342498,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T08:25:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/a